description:
This is a best 50 episodes (of 97) collection of the 1959-1961 black-and-white TV series &quot;One Step Beyond&quot; in compatible MP4 format for Google Chromecast.

The original source quality of the 30 minute episodes is, frankly, awful, so you must be tolerant of the poor archiving of some TV series from that era. This 4GB collection was optimzed (without notable quality loss) from a 10GB collection of AVI files.

-- Video: H264 ( 720 x 480 ) -- Audio: AAC (m4a) 44.1kHz
